OL,5, A group in Tayside has scrapped the    
OL,6, role of period dignity officer after   
OL,7, facing a backlash for appointing a man.
OL,9,FJason Grant's hiring sparked a heated  
OL,10,Fonline debate, with critics saying the 
OL,11,Fjob should have gone to a woman.       
OL,13,FThe area's period dignity working group
OL,14,Fsays the role will be discontinued     
OL,15,Ffollowing "threats and abuse" to those 
OL,16,Finvolved.                              
OL,18,FMr Grant was appointed to work with the
OL,19,Fgroup to ensure the legal right to free
OL,20,Fperiod products in public places.      
